Name:           edgex
Version:        0.7.1
Release:        1%{?dist}
License:        Apache-2.0
URL:            https://github.com/edgexfoundry/edgex-go
Group:          Applications/System
Vendor:         VMware, Inc.
Distribution:   Photon
